    <short-description type="string">
      A view dedicated for remote controling RC models and other flying objects.
    </short-description>

    <long-description type="string">
      RCView is a flightgear addon setting-up a new view which mimics
      the vision of a pilot remote controlling a plane.

      The RC pilot looks at the plane at all times and remains
      still. A configuration menu allows you to set your height and
      the distance at which you start remote controlling the target.

      During the flight, you can however jump to another location
      nearby the plane by pressing Alt-V under the RC View. This might
      be useful if you have miserably lost sight of your model or
      shamelessly crashed it in a nearby field.
    </long-description>

